    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of extraordinary caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, reflecting a level of preservation rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Every surface and mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standards, offering an ownership experience indistinguishable from new. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning driver who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
